an anomaly inside the prison has no basis.

229
00:18:43,664 --> 00:18:45,916
Uh, thank you all for coming
on such short notice.

230
00:18:46,333 --> 00:18:50,379
I just want to clarify my connection
with the escaped inmate, Edmundo Santiago.

231
00:18:50,462 --> 00:18:53,340
[tense music sting]

232
00:18:55,050 --> 00:18:56,385
14 years ago…

233
00:18:56,760 --> 00:19:00,514
<i>Edong Santiago brutally murdered</i>
<i>my friend Louisa Soria.</i>

234
00:19:01,723 --> 00:19:04,518
<i>My witness testimony</i>
<i>was what sent him to prison.</i>

235
00:19:05,102 --> 00:19:07,020
That's why he wants revenge.

236
00:19:07,104 --> 00:19:08,105
[sinister music playing]

237
00:19:08,188 --> 00:19:10,315
[Erica] <i>He is a very disturbed individual.</i>

238
00:19:10,983 --> 00:19:13,819
<i>So, everyone needs to be wary of him.</i>

