00:19:14,945 --> 00:19:18,282
<i>If you spot him,</i>
<i>report it to the police immediately.</i>

240
00:19:19,741 --> 00:19:21,285
<i>Edong, let's not drag this out.</i>

241
00:19:22,369 --> 00:19:23,787
<i>I'm the one you want.</i>

242
00:19:25,581 --> 00:19:27,040
<i>Don't involve anyone else.</i>

243
00:19:28,333 --> 00:19:29,459
<i>Don't hide.</i>

244
00:19:30,544 --> 00:19:32,254
<i>Don't be a coward.</i>

245
00:19:32,337 --> 00:19:33,589
[camera shutters clicking]

246
00:19:33,672 --> 00:19:35,591
I'm not afraid of you.

247
00:19:37,426 --> 00:19:40,512
[Erica] <i>If it's me</i>
<i>you want, I'm right here!</i>

248
00:19:42,890 --> 00:19:44,933
Face me instead!

249
00:19:45,017 --> 00:19:50,147
[music becomes dramatic]

250
00:20:15,672 --> 00:20:17,966
<i>That guy in the jacket is Edong Santiago!</i>

251
00:20:18,050 --> 00:20:21,136
<i>The police said</i>
<i>he escaped and wants revenge.</i>

252
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:23,972
<i>Aren't my mother and</i>
<i>her friends the ones who sent him to jail?</i>

253
00:20:24,056 --> 00:20:25,515
<i>I'm not afraid of you.</i>

254
00:20:25,599 --> 00:20:26,892
<i>Face me instead!</i>

255
00:20:26,975 --> 00:20:28,977
<i>With what she's doing,</i>
<i>she's only making Edong angrier!</i>

256
00:20:29,061 --> 00:20:31,521
<i>My priority is to stop Edong's plans.</i>

257
00:20:31,605 --> 00:20:33,815
<i>What if we were</i>
<i>wrong to have him imprisoned?</i>

258
00:20:33,899 --> 00:20:37,069
<i>We're not the ones to blame</i>
<i>when men lose control,</i>

259
00:20:37,152 --> 00:20:39,279
<i>get insecure, become angry, or go insane!</i>

260
00:20:39,363 --> 00:20:41,949
<i>So, whatever's going on in Edong's head,</i>
<i>that's his problem!</i>

261
00:20:42,032 --> 00:20:43,075
[screams] <i>Help me!</i>
